commit.message:
Use PyBytes instead of PyString regardless of Python version

* There's no need to use a conditional since PyBytes exists in
  both Python 2 and 3
* http://cython.readthedocs.io/en/latest/src/tutorial/strings.html
  #python-string-types-in-cython-code
* Also increment version to 0.1.8
